            <title>[CASSANDRA-18811] Set right client auth for creating SSL context in mTLS optional mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18811</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Adding a new value `optional` for require_client_auth in Encryption options. when require_client_auth is optional, the SSL context that is created will allow client connections that provide a client certificate along with the client connections that do not provide certificates.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
